OL,3,CCrews tackle fire at former convent in
OL,4,CSt Leonards
OL,6,FFirefighters have spent the night
OL,7,Ftackling a fire at a former convent in
OL,8,FSt Leonards.
OL,10,FThe blaze broke out at the property on
OL,11,FMagdalen Road, which is known as Hold
OL,12,FChild Jesus, on Thursday evening.
OL,14,FEast Sussex Fire and Rescue Service
OL,15,Fsaid, as of Friday morning, that one
OL,16,Ffire engine remained at the scene to
OL,17,Fmonitor and dampen down any hotspots.
OL,19,FThe service said that eight fire
OL,20,Fengines with relief crews were at the
OL,21,Fscene at the height of the blaze.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
